Package game.fields

Class PathField

java.lang.Object
game.fields.PathField
All Implemented Interfaces:
Field, Observable
Direct Known Subclasses:
EndField, StartField
public class PathField extends Object implements Field, Observable
Represents blank field to which FieldObjects can move. Changes can be registered by Observers.
Author:
Ondřej Vrána
